      <p class="text-2xl sm:max-w-2xl">
        At Mint Mantis, we are dedicated to advancing art and culture by guiding creatives to overcome the challenges of bringing their ideas to market. Through expert positioning, executional support, and strategic partnerships, we help artists and authors achieve self-sustaining success, all while staying true to the principles that guide our approach.
      </p>

